headline: Quarterra Multifamily Announces the Start of Leasing at Leya Apartments
summary: Quarterra Multifamily, a subsidiary of Lennar Corporation and a vertically integrated developer, property manager, and asset manager today announced the start of leasing at Leya Apartments, the newest luxury community in California's Bay Area.
